testcase.name: saving and loading an loaded collection in JSON doesn't loose data()
listActiveNotes returns no active notes stored when ArrayList is empty()
listNotesBySelectedPriority returns No Notes when ArrayList is empty()
listActiveNotes returns active notes when ArrayList has active notes stored()
listArchivedNotes returns no archived notes when ArrayList is empty()
listNotesBySelectedPriority returns all notes that match that priority when notes of that priority exist()
listNotesBySelectedPriority returns no notes when no notes of that priority exist()
listArchivedNotes returns archived notes when ArrayList has archived notes stored()
saving and loading an empty collection in JSON doesn't crash app()
